r />\n<br />\n<br />\n＃人性　難道有種尺度衡量？　理想　難道有一致的方向？<br />\n自然　難道最終汰弱留強？　仁義　難道牽強？<br />\n<br />\n站在這彎角　讓我很迷惘　步步也關鍵　回頭沒有岸<br />\n像半秒裡有千個選擇題　問哪個敢莽撞？<br />\n就算答對了九百九十題　尚有十個　仍是流著冷汗<br />\n<br />\n☆人性　難道這麼變幻無常？　理想　難道要舉世都景仰？<br />\n實情　難道似築了道圍牆？　期望　難道心傷？<br />\n<br />\n命運要考我　問我怎自處？　現在最需要　人治或法治？<br />\n用霎個眼已超過的限時　定永遠的正義<br />\n就看我應變　收放多自如　別再定格　無謂沉默對峙"},{"pid":"abf80cc146bedad580b81e3d126ab06851370fa0","tid":1110213,"uid":85694,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"一念無明"},{"pid":"7dcff6e4521df3c289593dd1427f8172a957959d","tid":1110213,"uid":122233,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T14:56:41.000Z","msg":"狂摸dick"},{"pid":"30cd60d6d8fdfbeb821e2dccdbd7db831d40569d","tid":1110213,"uid":194398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acea6612f8a5900d761627ed0a401db86117fb9f","tid":1110213,"uid":247824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1d76aac01bc0b2298bf5f2faad09e66680ec6c5","tid":1110213,"uid":236368,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T14:59:39.000Z","msg":"第一輯：做完愛&middot;回家之綠帽速遞<br />\n第二輯：做完愛&middot;回家之安心速遞"},{"pid":"a807d33139981c86ae07337d15ffc4bec62c53be","tid":1110213,"uid":181155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"心安理德"},{"pid":"09e65fd699fbe09fccadc8fb1898b1ceab641245","tid":1110213,"uid":191222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:08:26.000Z","msg":"綠的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe69005d30d4d02453157ae9672321caa4337a9","tid":1110213,"uid":187109,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:35:29.000Z","msg":"老襟唔易做<br />\n載得偷情人"},{"pid":"9c9d694bd9f5984ebcb80206d0901beb8bed5417","tid":1110213,"uid":187109,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20